'''Raymond L. Velasco''' was the author (credited as the "compiler") of the first edition of ''[[A Guide to the Star Wars Universe]]''.

The [[A Guide to the Star Wars Universe, Second Edition, Revised and Expanded|second]] and later editions of the book were written by [[Bill Slavicsek]]. These editions revised and expanded many of the entries in Velasco's edition, while omitting others completely.

